Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:04.92,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,面對認真地喜歡著自己的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.16,0:00:06.82,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我隨便就認定他是個下流胚子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:09.23,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有明確拒絕他的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:11.28,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人的距離也慢慢接近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.85,0:00:13.88,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,最後卻因為自己的任性而一刀兩斷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:17.51,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,心裡愧疚都想哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:21.73,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼東西 這什麼人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:22.87,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會在我的房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:25.34,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(930,984)}Holy healing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:25.34,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是霍利·西林格出品的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:27.62,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,治癒系絕倫美女人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:30.12,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要和她說話就會被治癒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:31.76,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 女朋友醬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:33.49,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.52,0:00:34.31,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,很恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:36.60,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:39.10,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對要從這種家裡搬出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.59,0:00:42.07,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒聽你說這話了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:45.69,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我已經決定要重新好好學習
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:48.01,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,為了這個我才選擇結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:52.32,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,木嶋應該很生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:06.35,aochan-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\blur4\c&HE8AC11&\pos(550,938)}小青{\r\blur4}只有{\blur4\c&HE8AC11&}妄想{\r\blur4}是不{\blur4\c&HE8AC11&}夠{\r\blur4}的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:07.39,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然木嶋沒有過來搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:13.87,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道這都是我自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:17.11,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但他現在連我的存在完全無視了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.39,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要去道歉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:20.31,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我該用什麼表情去面對他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.85,0:02:21.69,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,堀江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:25.02,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你跟木嶋發生了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:28.42,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他今天看上去心情超差
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.15,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,上原 離她遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:31.05,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:33.51,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要打擾堀江同學學習
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:36.65,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,「堀江同學」？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:38.73,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:39.71,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:40.44,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:44.19,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,心臟好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.39,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是平常的那種心動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:48.71,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,被人疏遠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:51.11,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,想到可能會被討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:53.96,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那種不安所帶來的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:59.16,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,再不學習的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:07.07,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:09.87,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,先做完我出的小測試
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:10.71,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:11.99,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:17.73,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.71,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在和木嶋交換的那本英語單詞本裡也出現過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:23.81,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他有沒有在用那本書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:26.97,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,應該沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:27.84,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.12,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:31.02,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我這笨蛋在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:33.20,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,別去想自己剛甩掉的那個男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.44,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你甩了木嶋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.21,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,為…為什麼你會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:38.96,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才說出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.37,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,與其說是甩掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:42.42,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說因為我還要學習
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:43.53,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是木嶋在的話我就沒法學習
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:44.85,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,木嶋會過來搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.23,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,木嶋還會說奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:49.04,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,木嶋會笑 木嶋會走動 木嶋會動…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:50.70,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,說一個木嶋就懲罰一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:52.21,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:57.24,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這打扮是怎麼回事 發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:58.11,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:03:59.03,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼懲罰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:02.36,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…木嶋他…木嶋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:03.37,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:07.10,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,矢部君 謝謝你照看青的學習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:09.44,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 畢竟我有很多等待的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:11.21,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,聽得我耳朵好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:14.01,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那個 青的樣子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:15.84,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個令人頭疼的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:18.33,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,原因似乎是一個名叫木嶋的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:19.66,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:24.65,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 只要做過一次男女之間的問題大多都能解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:25.52,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:27.87,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,對於青的監視我會繼續進行下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.15,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,請老師回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:35.81,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,得通知編輯部完稿的預定日期
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:39.67,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼矢部先生會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.16,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我被委託擔任青的家庭教師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:44.12,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你見不到她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:50.10,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚自己會妨礙堀江學習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:51.75,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:05.89,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想見她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.45,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,想再一次確認她的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.55,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這次還不行的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:12.57,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.06,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就去見她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:18.23,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:21.67,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 好好做個了斷對青的學習也有幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.64,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你去好好聽一下她的真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:39.26,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你完全沒法集中精神 就到這結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:43.90,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 木嶋這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.86,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為木嶋的關係我完全沒法學習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:46.96,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易甩了他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:48.86,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但木嶋那態度總會讓人想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.48,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人很在意 讓人很煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:56.26,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明必須好好學習的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:05:59.91,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.58,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 堀江
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:07.87,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼木嶋君會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.50,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,矢部先生讓我藏在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:13.16,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他說這樣就能聽到堀江的真心話了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:17.59,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,堀江想要獨自生活 並為此而努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:19.57,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這些我都聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:24.18,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,原來我差點就毀了你的人生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.98,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,堀江 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:30.18,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不會再妨礙你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:31.69,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來很謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:40.41,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:43.59,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說我和木嶋的關係到此為止嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.91,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,如我所期望的那樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:49.49,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,木嶋說他不會再妨礙我了所以要好好學習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.87,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然笑嘻嘻的但態度卻很強硬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.84,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然該生氣的時候會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:56.19,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但為了我的話還是會放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:57.80,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.94,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我是個人渣啊 我這種人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:15.76,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:24.23,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.34,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:33.02,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.66,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,內心不光在小鹿亂撞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.73,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,還有種心意相連的幸福感
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:43.25,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 他也想和我「相連」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:45.69,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微等一下 我現在身上全是汗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:46.62,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:47.93,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且打扮得也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:49.42,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,堀江穿什麼都很可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:53.49,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在非常地幸福 想摸你一下確認這都是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:54.88,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不願意的話你就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:56.56,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.30,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我說可以的話會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:00.15,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,會做嗎 我沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:04.09,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是木嶋是個處男 肯定不會做那麼厲害的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:05.69,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:09.25,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,直接摸？而且還是肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:11.48,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不行 而且我最近還胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:13.77,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 你很苗條啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.40,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,堀江？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:27.37,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,別只摸那裡 不還有其他地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:29.14,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:30.55,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在才問？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:31.68,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才不是同意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.51,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且平常不也都不經同意就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:36.29,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:41.06,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 如果不問清楚的話我會忍不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.63,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事我不也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:00.80,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:05.09,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事 而且我也拿到了很棒的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:06.39,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就給我扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:07.88,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣 別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:09.11,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.64,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然在堀江家裡這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.45,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,年輕氣盛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:15.95,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:18.45,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我有話要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:19.31,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.74,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,青很要強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:23.90,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,越想表達的話語 她越難以啟齒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:27.75,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以木嶋君你要引導她像年輕情侶那樣交往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:30.43,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,想做到哪步就做到哪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:31.35,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:32.91,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.00,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:37.82,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:39.93,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然發生了好多事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.27,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但這樣我和木嶋就已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:42.99,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,堀江
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:43.66,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:45.17,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很慶幸今天過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:47.25,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺跟你關係拉近了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:53.07,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我們早晚都要發展成那種關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:55.81,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 去買點新的內衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:57.56,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,必須準備好光溜溜的內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.09,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,伯父也讓我加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:02.38,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？爸爸就無所謂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:05.08,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啦 畢竟他很疼愛你這個女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:08.32,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓你和伯父失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:09.49,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.39,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 請和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:17.36,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是？在這個時機…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:20.99,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,一起學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.20,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:24.48,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要開始交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:25.47,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.61,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,學習？為啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.13,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候不是應該說交往啥的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:33.32,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也說過學生的本分就是學習
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:34.95,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,堀江也有自己的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:37.07,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,只想著自己的我有點太遜了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:39.17,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:42.10,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我在你考進目標大學之前都會忍住的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:46.10,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,結果這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:49.57,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的夢想裡加上了木嶋而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:50.00,aochan-sceen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz255.8\pos(815.6,180.8)}獨自生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.00,aochan-sceen2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz280.8\pos(1344,425.6)}在錄取之前會忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:54.42,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對要一次性考取上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:55.42,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:58.93,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:12:00.22,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}勃起勃起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:01.80,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想為你加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:02.61,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:04.35,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸不會加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:06.54,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我會親自為你製作體操服
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:07.92,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,わかんないこと多すぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:11.05,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,「わかろうとしてる時点ナンセンス」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:14.09,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,君の言葉、難しい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:17.30,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,君の魅力もワンダーランド
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:23.22,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,チャイムが鳴ったら逢いにゆくね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:26.39,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,夢中にさせて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:28.65,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}A i a i a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:32.48,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,100から始まる  カウント
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:37.66,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,君に近づけるリミット (Ah Ah Ah)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:41.37,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,じつに単純明快なココロ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:44.37,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,0に近い打率で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:49.92,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,青春のうちに射抜けるか！？ （Ah Ah Ah）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:53.42,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,じつに難しい僕らの関係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:56.88,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,WONDER WONDER WONDERFUL WONDER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:07.92,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白的事情太多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:11.05,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,「嘗試去了解時就已經顯得愚昧」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:14.09,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,你的話語 難以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:17.30,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,你的魅力就是仙境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:23.22,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,當鐘聲響起時  就想要去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:26.39,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我沉迷在你的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:32.48,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,從一百開始的倒計時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:37.66,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,與你接近的極限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:41.37,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,實在是單純明快的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:44.37,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是精確度接近於零的命中率
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:49.92,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,也能在青春中命中你嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:53.42,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的關係非常複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:56.88,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,奇妙 奇妙 絕妙的奇蹟
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:08.18,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}頭の中いっぱいに溢れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:13.90,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}君のことで占拠率１２０％
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:18.40,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}純粋無垢なこの気持ぎゅっと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:23.37,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}投げつけたり　伝えたい全部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:29.41,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}恋だって気づく前から
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:35.50,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}君に全部ごと惹かれていたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:41.05,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}そうとも知らずに　そうやってまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:48.77,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}無邪気な笑顔見せるから困ったもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:52.19,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}気づかないかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:08.18,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}你在我的腦中充溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:13.90,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}120%占據了我的腦海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:18.40,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}這份純粹無垢的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:23.37,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}想要全部傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:29.41,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}在發現這份戀情之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:35.50,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}就已經被你深深吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:41.05,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}在不知不覺中我依舊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:48.77,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}以天真無邪的笑容面對你 是否感到困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:52.19,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}能否發現我的心意？
